    <!--
        PLAYER PRESETS
        ==============

        These appear as selectable starting points in the Religion/Ideology wizard.
        Selecting a preset pre-populates meme selections — all memes remain fully editable.
        Presets are collapsed by default in the wizard UI.

        If no presets are defined for a type (Religion/Ideology), the preset section
        is hidden entirely in the wizard.

        This file ships empty by default. Add your own presets below.

        ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

        FIELDS:

            defName           Unique identifier (required).
            label             Display name shown in the preset card (required).
            description       Tooltip description shown on hover (optional).
            presetType        "Religion" or "Ideology" — which wizard step this appears in.
            structureMeme     The foundation meme defName (required — exactly one).
            normalMemes       Additional meme defNames (optional — can be empty).
            iconPath          Texture path for the preset card icon (optional).
                              If not set, the structure meme's icon is used.

        ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

        AVAILABLE RELIGION STRUCTURE MEMES:

            Structure_Animist           — Animism, nature spirits
            Structure_TheistEmbodied    — Embodied theism, god walks among mortals
            Structure_TheistAbstract    — Abstract theism, distant unknowable god
            Structure_Archist           — Archotech worship, machine gods
            Structure_OriginChristian   — Christian-origin theology
            Structure_OriginIslamic     — Islamic-origin theology
            Structure_OriginHindu       — Hindu-origin theology
            Structure_OriginBuddhist    — Buddhist-origin theology

        AVAILABLE RELIGION NORMAL MEMES:

            Proselytizer, Blindsight, HighLife, PainIsVirtue, Cannibal, Nudism,
            TreeConnection, Darkness, AnimalPersonhood, Tunneler,
            MaleSupremacy, FemaleSupremacy, HumanPrimacy, NaturePrimacy, FleshPurity

        AVAILABLE IDEOLOGY STRUCTURE MEMES:

            Structure_Ideological       — Rationalist social philosophy

        AVAILABLE IDEOLOGY NORMAL MEMES:

            Transhumanist, Supremacist, Loyalist, Guilty,
            Individualist, Collectivist, Rancher, Raider

        ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

        EXAMPLES (uncomment to use):

        Religion preset:
        <IdeoRework.ReligionPresetDef>
            <defName>PlayerPreset_DruidCircle</defName>
            <label>Druid Circle</label>
            <description>A nature-focused spiritual order that venerates the old groves.</description>
            <presetType>Religion</presetType>
            <structureMeme>Structure_Animist</structureMeme>
            <normalMemes>
                <li>NaturePrimacy</li>
                <li>TreeConnection</li>
            </normalMemes>
        </IdeoRework.ReligionPresetDef>

        Ideology preset:
        <IdeoRework.ReligionPresetDef>
            <defName>PlayerPreset_MeritocraticUnion</defName>
            <label>Meritocratic Union</label>
            <description>A society that values achievement and individual excellence above all.</description>
            <presetType>Ideology</presetType>
            <structureMeme>Structure_Ideological</structureMeme>
            <normalMemes>
                <li>Individualist</li>
            </normalMemes>
        </IdeoRework.ReligionPresetDef>

        Preset with custom icon:
        <IdeoRework.ReligionPresetDef>
            <defName>PlayerPreset_TechCult</defName>
            <label>Techno-Cult</label>
            <description>Technology is sacred. The flesh is weak.</description>
            <presetType>Religion</presetType>
            <structureMeme>Structure_Archist</structureMeme>
            <normalMemes>
                <li>Transhumanist</li>
            </normalMemes>
            <iconPath>UI/Icons/Meme/Transhumanist</iconPath>
        </IdeoRework.ReligionPresetDef>
    -->
</Defs>
